dc_description_s: Relief shown by 10 feet contours and spot heights. Map shows roads, major buildings, vegetation, cemeteries, churches, mosques, and other important features. Includes guide to numbered features, index to streets, and boundary sketch map. "12-65 Printed by Army Map Service, Corps of Engineers." "NSN 7643014045172." "DMA stock no. Y932XJINJA." "Prepared by the Army Map Service (AM), Corps of Engineers, U.S. Army, Washington D. C. Compiled in 1965 from Jinja, 1:10,000. The Department of Lands and Surveys, Uganda, compiled 1963 (topographic map, controlled ground survey, revised 1962, reliability good). Planimetric detail revised by photo-planimetric methods. Aerial photography Oct. 1963. Map not field checked."
